import React from 'react';
import { useLocation } from 'react-router-dom';
import {
  Box,
  Typography,
  Button,
  Container,
  Paper,
  Grid
} from '@mui/material';
import MetadataIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Description';
import CoverIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Image';

const TaskDashboard = () => {
  const location = useLocation();
  const bookName = location.state?.bookName || 'Il patto';

  return (
    <Box sx={{ backgroundColor: '#F8F9FA', minHeight: '100vh' }}>
      <Container maxWidth="lg" sx={{ py: 4 }}>
        <Box sx={{ mb: 4 }}>
          <Typography 
            variant="subtitle2" 
            color="text.secondary"
            sx={{ mb: 1 }}
          >
            NOVEMBER, 2024
          </Typography>
          <Typography 
            variant="h5" 
            component="h1"
            sx={{ 
              fontWeight: 500,
              color: 'text.primary'
            }}
          >
            {bookName}
          </Typography>
        </Box>

        <Grid container spacing={3}>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <Paper 
              sx={{ 
                p: 3,
                '&:hover': {
                  boxShadow: '0px 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08)',
                  cursor: 'pointer'
                }
              }}
            >
              <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'flex-start' }}>
                <Box 
                  sx={{ 
                    mr: 3,
                    backgroundColor: '#F8F9FF',
                    borderRadius: '12px',
                    p: 2
                  }}
                >
                  <MetadataIcon sx={{ fontSize: 48, color: 'primary.main' }} />
                </Box>
                <Box sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
                  <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                    Craft and optimize metadata
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary" sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
                    I'll provide tailored suggestions to optimize your metadata for improved organic visibility and sales in stores.
                  </Typography>
                  <Button
                    variant="outlined"
                    color="primary"
                  >
                    PREVIEW
                  </Button>
                </Box>
              </Box>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <Paper 
              sx={{ 
                p: 3,
                '&:hover': {
                  boxShadow: '0px 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08)',
                  cursor: 'pointer'
                }
              }}
            >
              <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'flex-start' }}>
                <Box 
                  sx={{ 
                    mr: 3,
                    backgroundColor: '#F8F9FF',
                    borderRadius: '12px',
                    p: 2
                  }}
                >
                  <CoverIcon sx={{ fontSize: 48, color: 'primary.main' }} />
                </Box>
                <Box sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
                  <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                    Create a cover image
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary" sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
                    I'll choose scenes based on your manuscript that effectively represent its content. I'll then generate cover images for each scene, which you can modify, request additional ones, and download in various formats.
                  </Typography>
                  <Button
                    variant="outlined"
                    color="primary"
                  >
                    PREVIEW
                  </Button>
                </Box>
              </Box>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>

        <Box sx={{ mt: 4, textAlign: 'center' }}>
          <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
            © 2024 Marco Luigi Palma - All rights reserved.
          </Typography>
          <Box sx={{ mt: 1 }}>
            <Button color="primary" size="small">View Privacy Policy</Button>
            <Button color="primary" size="small">Terms & Conditions</Button>
          </Box>
        </Box>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default TaskDashboard;
